{"tid":113530,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"93－98 小圈子開心吹水活動 Whatsapp  Group又招人喇","createTime":"2017-02-09T05:01:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T13:34:45.000Z","uid":68021,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd116e3939cdefe731e421584602d754a02fa1d2","tid":113530,"uid":68021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T05:01:44.000Z","msg":"又係我喇 <span style=\"color: red;\">Happy Group </span>Admin<br />\n由於最近好多巴絲都潛左水既關係 又係時候上黎連登搵新血喇<br />\n<br />\n歡迎活躍既巴絲加入  成日唔得閒吹水既巴絲可以按上一頁離開，麻煩哂<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">呢個群既人數會維持係30人以內 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n因為每一個成員都好重要，同埋個group注重既係warm既氣氛！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於巴絲們最關心既男女比例，當然想盡量平均啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s. 填左form之後請耐心等候，admin唔係每一刻都mon住有幾多人交form <br />\n<br />\n填form: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd1-dI4dUdaAS4nVE36-Fl8_AhXeMM6pJkElmD726Nmliz8zg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSd1-dI4dUdaAS4nVE36-Fl8_AhXeMM6pJkElmD726Nmliz8zg%2Fviewform&d=5W7Dp6DGRi9eT2AMHrnJu9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=28b68f18\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd1-dI4dUdaAS4nVE36-Fl8_AhXeMM6pJkElmD726Nmliz8zg/viewform</a>"},{"pid":"ab1aa58e727e1d5f368f857c0f5f8530e16b1bb7","tid":113530,"uid":68021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T11:08:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18184957ffe4103f210e4a07695cf79517b8a88e","tid":113530,"uid":68021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T05:24:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce20df50ed7d8cff88bb456c355f9dd22db35e10","tid":113530,"uid":68021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-